The paper deals with data structures and algorithms for spatial data sets, which suggests that it could belong to several sub-categories. The use of hash filters and range queries suggests that it could belong to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) or cs.DB (Databases). The mention of GIS applications suggests that it could belong to cs.CG (Computational Geometry). The use of bitwise operations suggests that it could belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.DM (Data Mining).
